title: BRIEF-Nokia Enters Into Exclusive Negotiations For The Sale Of Its Digital Health Business

organizations.name: sale of its digital health business reuters

text:
May 2, 2018 / 9:14 AM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Nokia Enters Into Exclusive Negotiations For The Sale Of Its Digital Health Business Reuters Staff
May 2 (Reuters) - Nokia Oyj:
* NOKIA ENTERS INTO EXCLUSIVE NEGOTIATIONS FOR THE SALE OF ITS DIGITAL HEALTH BUSINESS
* NOKIA - PLANS TO SELL DIGITAL HEALTH BUSINESS TO ÉRIC CARREEL, CO-FOUNDER AND FORMER CHAIRMAN OF WITHINGS
* NOKIA - PLANNED SALE OF DIGITAL HEALTH WOULD BE PART OF CO’S SHIFT TO BECOME BUSINESS-TO-BUSINESS & LICENSING CO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
